article_id:1463,category_name:Events,title_name:A Raid Event Revival, A Splash of Adventure, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/464cdf636d86d236a0457b4bba517417.png,message:<div>The A Splash of Adventure raid event revival will begin <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1595224800"></span>!</div><div>During this event, you can use co-op play to fight against the flame-attuned raid boss.</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/464cdf636d86d236a0457b4bba517417.png"></div><div>Even warriors need a vacation every now and again! The prince and friends have come to a scenic island to get the most out of the sun&#39;s shining rays and bright blue sea, but a secret is waiting for them! There is a treasure hidden somewhere on the island! Guided by a treasure map and joined by a dragon of azure flame, the prince and friends encounter a mysterious and powerful ocean fiend...<br><br>Notes:<br>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate in event quests.<br>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1594965600,update_time1594965816